From 06f7c63155cecd11a2d15091576167356f054adc Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Anson Huang <Anson.Huang@nxp.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Nov 2017 21:46:22 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 2809/5242] MLK-16833 ARM64: dts: freescale: imx8mq: enable
 over-drive mode by default

commit  9a1074ffacbed58f9df3d03da88d0a8bae90407e from
https://source.codeaurora.org/external/imx/linux-imx.git

As all the EVK boards except A0 support over-drive mode,
so enable it in default EVK board dtb and remove over
drive mode dtb.

Signed-off-by: Anson Huang <Anson.Huang@nxp.com>
Reviewed-by: Bai Ping <ping.bai@nxp.com>
Signed-off-by: Meng Li <Meng.Li@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile             |    1 -
 .../arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8mq-evk-od.dts |   51 --------------------
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8mq-evk.dts   |   45 ++++++++---------
 3 files changed, 23 insertions(+), 74 deletions(-)
 delete mode 100644 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/fsl-imx8mq-evk-od.dts

